{{Infobox football biography | name = Adnan Haxhaj | image = | image_size = | fullname = Adnan Haxhaj | birth_date = {{birth date and age|1988|09|16|df=y}} | birth_place = [[Vushtrri]], [[SFR Yugoslavia]] | height = | currentclub = [[KF Drenica|Drenica]] | clubnumber = 5 | position = [[Defender (association football)|Centre back]] | youthyears1 = | youthclubs1 = | years1 = 2009–2015 | clubs1 = [[FC Prishtina]] | caps1 = 40+ | goals1 = 2+ | years2 = 2015–2016 | clubs2 = [[Vllaznia Shkodër]] | caps2 = 1 | goals2 = 0 | years3 = 2018– | clubs3 = [[KF Drenica|Drenica]] | caps3 = 0 | goals3 = 0 | nationalyears1 = | nationalteam1 =| nationalcaps1 = | nationalgoals1 = | pcupdate = {{date|2014-10-05}} | ntupdate = {{date|2013-10-15}} }}
'''Adnan Haxhaj''' (born 16 September 1988 in [[Vushtrri]]) is a Kosovar–[[Albanian people|Albanian]] [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)|centre back]] for [[Vllaznia Shkodër]] in the [[Albanian Superliga]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://telesport.al/vllaznia-merr-mbnrojtesin-e-prishtines-adnan-haxhaj/ |title=Vllaznia merr mbrojtësin e Prishtinës, Adnan Haxhaj |date=14 July 2015 |accessdate=1 September 2015|language=Albanian |author=Alfred Lleshi |work=Telesport }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://telesport.al/adnan-haxhaj-ja-pse-e-lashe-prishtinen-dhe-zgjodha-vllaznine/ |title=Adnan Haxhaj: Ja pse e lashë Prishtinën dhe zgjodha Vllazninë |date=14 July 2015 |accessdate=1 September 2015|language=Albanian |author=Eduard Ilnica |work=Telesport }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.telegrafi.com/sport/haxhaj-rinovon-me-prishtinen-92-0-2741.html |title=Haxhaj rinovon me Prishtinën |date=15 January 2014 |accessdate=1 September 2015|language=Albanian |author= |work=Telegrafi }}</ref>
